import { Paper, Stack } from "@mui/material"
import { colors } from "../../utils/CustomTheme"
import { puzzleInputs } from "../../utils/PuzzleInputs"
import { PuzzleInput } from "../Atoms"
import { usePuzzleState } from "../Atoms/PuzzleInput"
const HomePage = () => {
    const puzzleState = usePuzzleState(puzzleInputs[14].example)
    return <Paper square sx={{ paddingBottom: 1080, width: "100vw" }}>
        <Stack justifyContent="center" alignItems="center">
            <PuzzleInput puzzleState sx={{ width: "80vw", border: `1px solid ${colors.saffron}` }} />
        </Stack>
    </Paper>
}

export default HomePage
